umbutis]] (July 1, 1998&nbsp;\u2013 Dec 31, 1999), (Jan 1, 2003&nbsp;\u2013 Dec 31, 2003)\n*{{flagicon|Belarus}} [[Vladimir Gevorkyan]] (Jan 1, 2003&nbsp;\u2013 Jan 13, 2004)\n*{{flagicon|Belarus}} [[Oleg Volokh]] ''(interim)'' (May 14, 2004&nbsp;\u2013 May 27, 2004)\n*{{flagicon|Belarus}} [[Sergei Borovsky]] (Sept 3, 2004&nbsp;\u2013 Dec 31, 2004)\n*{{flagicon|Belarus}} [[Oleg Volokh]] (Jan 1, 2006&nbsp;\u2013 May 11, 2006)\n*{{flagicon|Belarus}} [[Mikhail Markhel]] (May 16, 2006&nbsp;\u2013 Dec 31, 2006)\n*{{flagicon|Belarus}} [[Aleksandr Sednev]] (Jan 1, 2009&nbsp;\u2013 Nov 30, 2011)\n*{{flagicon|Belarus}} [[Sergey Yaromko]] (Jan 1, 2012&nbsp;\u2013 July 21, 2012)\n*{{flagicon|Ukraine}} [[Vitaliy Pavlov (footballer, born 1965)|Vitaliy Pavlov]] ''(caretaker)'' (July 21, 2012&nbsp;\u2013 July 23, 2012)\n*{{flagicon|Belarus}} [[Aleksandr Sednev]] (July 23, 2012&nbsp;\u2013 December 31, 2015)\n*{{flagicon|Ukraine}} [[Vitaliy Pavlov (footballer, born 1965)|Vitaliy Pavlov]] (January 1, 2016&nbsp;\u2013 )\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.fcbelshina.by/ Official website]\n\n{{Belarusian Premier League teamlist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Belshina Bobruislk}}\n[[Category:Football clubs in Belarus]]\n[[Category:Association football clubs established in 1976]]\n[[Category:Babruysk]]\n[[Category:1976 establishments in Belarus]]\n", "name_user": "Serbianboy87", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/FC_Belshina_Bobruisk"}
